<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ại̹laha kulĩ niʿ̊maẗiⁿ
 nasẖ̊kuru kulã ḥīn̊
 wanukẖ̊biru bifaḍ̊lika
 waḥubĩka ạltẖãmīn̊

[V2]
 2- ạảf̊ḍāluka lanā badat̊
 fī rabĩnā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 daʿaẘtanā limaj̊dika
 wanūrika ạl̊ʿajīb̊

[V3]
 3- ṣir̊nā ʿarūsaⁿạ lạib̊nika
 biạl̊ḥaqĩ wālṣĩd̊qi
 naḥ̊nu ạlãdẖīna tih̊nā fī
 mafāriqi ạlṭũr̊qi

[V4]
 4- qad̊ kunãạ qab̊lạaⁿ fī ạl̊kẖaṭā
 wālsẖãrĩ wālẓãlạm̊
 fī ạb̊nika qad̊ ạảʿ̊ṭaẙtanā
 ạltãb̊rīra wālsãlạm̊

[V5]
 5- fayā lahā min̊ daʿ̊waẗiⁿ
 sāmīaẗi ạl̊maqām̊
 fīhā lanā kulũ ạl̊gẖinay̱
 wāl̊maj̊du wālsãlạm̊

[V6]
 6- wakulũ dẖā biạlnĩʿ̊maẗi
 ại̹lahanā ạlạảmīn̊
 fāl̊ḥam̊da nuh̊dī lạis̊mika
 wāl̊maj̊da kulã ḥīn̊</lyrics>
<aka>ạ̹lh kl nʿmẗ</aka>
<title>ạlh kl nʿmẗ</title>
</song>